This project is about the LED Control using Raspberry pi in LINUX KERNEL MODULE In C Programming language
STEPS:
Install the raspberry pi installer to your device 
Download and install the raspberry pi driver, full version is always better.
Save the code files using terminal or in a specific accessible folder
Use "CHMOD 777 Filename" if any code asks any permission 
Connect the LED with a resistor to the pins of raspberry pi (VCC and GND)
Make file is also given so just execute them with Makeall commamnd 
and execute the main file using ./filename 
Application program is also given if necessary
REFERENCE FOR INSTALLATION PDF IS INLCUDED IN THE ATTACHMENT
